<body>
    <h1>User Data Deletion Instructions</h1>
    <p>
        If you would like to delete your account or any personal data collected by this application, please follow these steps:
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li>Send an email to <strong>your-email@example.com</strong> with the subject line "Data Deletion Request".</li>
        <li>Include your account ID, username, or any identifying information so we can locate your data.</li>
        <li>We will confirm your request within 7 days and delete your data from our records within 30 days, unless required by law to retain it.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        If you have logged in via Facebook, you can also remove the app directly from your Facebook settings:
    </p>
    <ol>
        <li>Go to <a href="https://www.facebook.com/settings?tab=business_tools" target="_blank">Facebook Settings</a>.</li>
        <li>Find and select our application in the list.</li>
        <li>Click “Remove” to revoke our access to your data.</li>
    </ol>
    <p>
        For any further assistance, please contact us at <strong>your-email@example.com</strong>.
    </p>
</body>
